artworks.art_title: The Watermill with the Great Red Roof
artworks.description: Landscape painting featuring a wavy tree tree in the foreground and a watermill with a red roof adjacent to a river at right. Colors are subdued earth tones, the foliage a dark green and the river a muddy brown. Water flows through the mill wheel under a cloudy sky of gray and blue. Three individuals can be seen in the distance at left.
Interior of warm colored room, woman sits on balcony, ocean behind her.
Painting of Judith, naked, holding sword, with head of Holophernes.

artworks.art_title: Fishing Boats with Hucksters Bargaining for Fish
artworks.description: Large marine landscape of boats on rough waves, storm clouds.
Large English country landscape painting, farmers with horses, green trees.

artworks.artist: Real Fabbrica della porcellana di Capodimonte
artworks.description: Porcelain pitcher with coral handle, encrusted shells, gold interior.

artworks.art_title: Lady Sarah Bunbury Sacrificing to the Graces
artworks.description: Large painting, woman in pink dress in front of classical sculpture, shrine.
Painting of hanging, ripped apart animal carcass with seated man.
Painting of a woman and an older white man holding a pitchfork, both seen from the waist up. They stand side by side with stern expressions, in front of a white house with a peaked roof.
Shiny dark sculpture of nude woman reclining on stone pedestal.
Blue and brown Cubist painting of Picasso with painterǳ palette.

artworks.art_title: Champs de Mars: The Red Tower
artworks.description: Cubist painting of distorted gray Paris buildings, red Eiffel Tower.
Gold folded tall screen with red flowers, green maize plants.
Cubist style painting of seated woman, with brown, blue, green shapes.
Abstract painting in various bright colors—yellow, blue, red, green, orange, pink—with lines indicating building-like structures as well as canons in the lower right corner.

artworks.art_title: Salome with the Head of Saint John the Baptist
artworks.description: Large painting of woman, in gold and pink dress, placing severed head on platter.
Dark colored sculpture of muscular man standing in a contorted pose.
Painting of coastal town seen through leafy branches, blue sea and sky fill background.

artworks.art_title: Karttikeya, Commander of the Divine Army, Seated on a Peacock
artworks.description: Gray statue with multiple heads and arms seated on Peacock.

Painted portrait dominated by loose, large brushstrokes of a woman, seen from the back, wearing a gauzy white off-the-shoulder dress and black choker, blond hair swept up, examining herself in a mirror at left. The background is a feathered swirl suggesting floral pattern in cool pale tones of gray, purple, pink, and blue.
Impressionist painting of woman wearing green dress trying on hats.
Impressionist painting of two girls on balcony, bright flower hat, knitting basket.
Painting of a beach on a cloudy day with several sailboats on the water, a few rowboats on the shore, and two groupings of people on the sand.

artworks.art_title: Mural Fragment Depicting a Maguey Bloodletting Ritual
artworks.description: Frament of a mural from the city of Teotihuacan mural painted in red and white tones that depicts a ritual figure with speach scroll and scatting sacred bjects.
Opulently dressed light-skinned man and woman drink at a small table. A mirror behind them reflects a crowd. Her blue dress and dark hat dominate.

Painting of a performance inside a circus ring. A man wearing a suit holds a whip in his hand and looks towards a woman with red hair riding a gray horse and wearing a green dress. Audience members wearing suits and top hats watch from red and white benches on the side.
St. George on white horse, piercing green, gold dragon

Life-size painting of an urban scene in Paris. A man in a top hat holding an umbrella and a woman in a long fashionable dark dress walk arm in arm toward the viewer as other city dwellers with umbrellas walk in various directions across cobblestone roads and sidewalks.

artworks.art_title: Virgin and Child with the Young Saint John the Baptist
artworks.description: Vividly colored painting of Virgin Mary with baby Jesus and baby John the Baptist.
Oil painting in cartoon style of gigantic, close-up brushstroke of paint, blue spatter.
Large, dark painting of Jesus sitting with three standing soldiers.

artworks.art_title: Friar Pedro Shoots El Maragato as His Horse Runs Off
artworks.artist: Francisco José de Goya y Lucientes
artworks.description: Small painting, friar shoots man with yellow pants as horse runs off.

artworks.art_title: The Frugal Meal, from The Saltimbanques
artworks.description: Blue-green print of thin man and woman seated at table with empty plates and glasses.
Painting of four women with blue shawls walking near red fence.
Chalk drawing with red and black shading of man carrying crate and pack.
Large bowl completely covered in scenes of battles on land and sea.
A young woman in a dark hat and coat with light ruffled collar sits reading a large periodical held up in her gloved hands. Flowers and foliage are suggested behind her.
Painting of bedroom, blue walls, green window, tan bed, red bedding.
Surrealist painting of cannon, artichokes, clock, train, desolate backdrop.

artworks.art_title: Mirror Frame with Tree of Life Motif
artworks.description: Tan jade frame with ruby, diamond, emerald flower designs.
Pale silhouettes of two flowering branches.
Collage style painting on glass, purple figure with large nose.
Ink drawing of landscape with trees, houses, two seated figures.

Painting in shades of dark red, brown, and black, depicting figures crowded in a doorway of a small hut, engaged in conflict. One man looms in front of the doorway with a stoic expression, and four other figures kneel and stand beside him. One points a sword at his face.
Serene red-haired woman, framed with allegorical symbols of red bird, sundial.
Greenish brown ceramic kettle with floral and geometric designs.
Oil portrait with man in suit, dim green background.
Small painting of woman in pink and black sitting on park bench.
Vertical black sculpture of rounded and rectangular shapes, suggesting a human figure.
Surrealist painting of miniature train exiting fireplace mid-air, large mirror over mantle.

artworks.art_title: Landscape with Saint John on Patmos
artworks.description: Painting of Greek landscape, classical architecture, yellow, red robed man reading.

artworks.art_title: The Night is Stirring (La nuit remue)
artworks.description: Blue abstract painting with gray, red, black vertical blurry design.

artworks.art_title: Processional Cross with Saint Mary Magdalene and a Blessed Hermit
artworks.description: Framed gold panel of the Crucifixion, kneeling figures, flying angels.
Somewhat abstract and geometric painting of a clearly discernable, light-skinned female dancer, standing in profile, swaths of white lace fabric adorning and radiating from her, a fan in her hand.

artworks.art_title: Incense Burner in the Form of a Duck
artworks.description: Porcelain sculpture with pale-blue glaze, shape of a duck atop a lotus flower.

In a beige room, a group of light-skinned men of various ages and a young boy clap as a figure in tattered clothing at center, his back to the viewer, dances and holds a tin cup in the air. At dark figure in shadows looks on from the far-right corner.

artworks.art_title: The Holy Family with Saints Elizabeth and John the Baptist
artworks.description: Large painting of Holy Family: Mary in red, holding baby Jesus.
Small white porcelain cups with circular patterns and no handles.
Painting of woman, arms crossed on brown desk, staring at goldfish.

artworks.art_title: Shiva as Lord of the Dance (Nataraja)
artworks.description: A bronze sculpture of the Hindu divinity Shiva. Shiva, who has two pairs of arms, is depicted dancing inside of a circular ring. Balancing on one leg, Shiva gestures his arms to the side and front, as his loose locks of hair flow behind him.

artworks.art_title: View of Delphi with a Procession
artworks.description: A work made of oil on canvas.

artworks.art_title: Triptych with Scenes from the Life of Christ
artworks.description: Three connected ivory panels carved with scenes from the life of Jesus.
Large painting of soldier asleep outdoors surrounded by two women and a cupid.

artworks.art_title: Under the Wave off Kanagawa (Kanagawa oki nami ura), also known as The Great Wave, from the series Thirty-Six Views of Mount Fuji (Fugaku sanjūrokkei)
artworks.description: A crashing wave looms over two small ships, Mount Fuji in the background.

A female figure with a round face in a full orange robe is bent almost wearily as she rides a horse. White pigment has worn away on the horse, and orange has worn from her robe, revealing a terracotta tone.
Cubist painting of woman, bright yellow, green, purple colors.

artworks.art_title: A Sunday on La Grande Jatte — 1884
artworks.description: Large painting of people in a crowded park, brushstrokes are dots.

Painting of man who is seated with his hands over his lap. He is dressed in prayer clothes, with a white shawl draped over his head and shoulders. His facial features and hands are slightly distorted, and the background is an abstract pattern of black and white.
A light-skinned woman in a long, shiny white dress sits at a desk reading a book. The book is propped on a large red pillow. Her head is propped in her hand.
A man with sparse brown facial hair stands in a full-length black robe on a multicolored tiled floor, a white and brown dog behind him.
An abstract steel sculpture of welded metal parts suggesting a human figure with long, thin legs and a bulkier shoulder area.
Black and white photograph of women, lips pursed, against wood paneled wall.
Painting, mostly in shades of blue, of a thin, bent, older man wearing ragged clothes and sitting cross-legged playing a guitar positioned upright in his lap.
Dark stone sculpture of Buddha sitting cross-legged, hands in lap, eyes closed.

artworks.art_title: Madame de Pastoret and Her Son
artworks.description: Large painting of young woman in white dress sitting next to crib.
A work made of pen and black ink on ivory laid paper.
Dark portrait of an older light-skinned women with dark hair in a black dress and white collar, her hair pinned up. Her face is in partial shadow.
Abstract painting in predominant shades of blue, green, and black, featuring diagonal bands of color and undulating lines.

A light-skinned woman, the bodice of her mauve dress pulled down, lounges against a rock, her arm extended on it. A child, mostly nude, stands in front of her looking downward while two men in her party, largely in shadow, lean toward each other as if in conversation.
Watercolor, boat debris and dark skinned man lie on beach, dark sky in background.
Painting of two fishermen in small wooden boat on rocky seas.
Painting of the Annunciation, dove flying above Mary with angel.
Painting of woman with orange cardigan leaning over desk covered in playing cards.

artworks.art_title: Portrait of Jean Gross (recto); Coat of Arms of Jean Gros (verso)
artworks.description: Painted dark colored portrait of man, hands in prayer.
Large ebony cabinet with white designs, ivory figures, clock.

artworks.art_title: Arrangement in Flesh Color and Brown: Portrait of Arthur Jerome Eddy
artworks.description: Very dark painting of a light-skinned, mostly clean-shaven young man in dark suit and dark full-length coat, holding a rolled-up paper and gloves.
Dark portrait of older woman in black dress with lace collar, flowers.
Large abstract painting with red, blue, white, black shapes.
Abstract painting with soft shapes of brown, pink, yellow, red.

Painting depicting the god Hercules confronting the Hydra, a mythical creature. Amidst towering, rocky cliffs, Hercules stands on the left of the painting, dressed in clothing that exposes his figure. He looks to the right, where the seven-headed hydra rears up, bearing its teeth. A nude figure of a woman is on the ground in front of the Hydra, and an orange sun peeks from behind red clouds in the background.

artworks.art_title: Henri Degas and His Niece Lucie Degas (The Artist's Uncle and Cousin)
artworks.description: Impressionist painting of seated man, girl with brown, black hues.

artworks.art_title: Arrival of the Normandy Train, Gare Saint-Lazare
artworks.description: Loosely painted image of an open-air train station. On the right, a parked train gives off an enormous plumb of white smoke, making the scene look as though it were full of clouds. A huddled mass of barely discernible people crowd around the train on both sides of the tracks. Blue, green, and gray tones dominate.
Painting of a pond seen up close spotted with thickly painted pink and white water lilies and a shadow across the top third of the picture.
Tall red-brown mahogany clock with brass trim.
Charcoal drawing of young woman wearing headscarf, staring out expressionless.

artworks.art_title: The Bay of Marseille, Seen from L'Estaque
artworks.description: Impressionist sea landscape, tan houses, blue ocean, distant mountains.

artworks.art_title: The Beheading of Saint John the Baptist
artworks.description: A headless figure leans out of the first-floor window of a light-colored stone building from which two iron bars have been detatched, his blood spurting to the ground. A figure bends to collect the head while another looks away to sheath a long sword. From right, a robed man beholds the guesome scene.
Half circle of fabric, embroidered with Virgin Mary, saints, prophets, and plant motif.
Large painting, standing man blue turtleneck, sitting woman with white collar.
Gold knife with figure on handle, round turquoise inlays on crown.
